miscConds.notes:
Attend and complete a batters treatment class program; 
No possession or consumption of alcohol; 
No possession or consumption of a controlled substance without a prescription and if have a physician's prescription, take it within therapeutic range;  
Submit to mental health assessment selected by DOC;
AODA and follow the requirements;
Pay for any therapy or treatment for RAL.  Pepin County Victim Witness Coordinator to find out if there is a need.
